doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    title File Metadata Microservice
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto', rel='stylesheet')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='style.css')
  body
    h1 API Project: File Metadata Microservice <br><br>
    h2 User Story
    ol 
      li I can submit a form object that includes a file upload.
      li The from file input field has the "name" attribute set to "upfile". We rely on this in testing.
      li When I submit something, I will receive the file name, and size in bytes within the JSON response.
    h2 Usage
    p Please Upload a File ...
    form(enctype="multipart/form-data" method="POST" action="/api/fileanalyse" target="_blank")
      input(id="inputfield" type="file" name="upfile")
      input(id="button" type="submit" value="Upload")